#~ "los usuarios de <tt>devfs</tt> deberán convertir sus sistemas manualmente "
#~ "antes de arrancar con un núcleo de &releasename;."

# type: <p></p>
#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you see the string 'devfs' in <file>/proc/mounts</file>, you are most "
#~ "likely using <tt>devfs</tt>. Any configuration files that reference "
#~ "<tt>devfs</tt>-style names will need to be adjusted to use <package>udev</"
