#~ "<package>exim</package> installation to <package>exim4</package> "
#~ "manually. Since <package>exim4</package> is already part of "
#~ "&oldreleasename;, you can choose to do the upgrade on your "
#~ "&oldreleasename; system before the upgrade to &releasename;, or after the "
#~ "&releasename; upgrade at your convenience. Just remember that your old "
#~ "<package>exim</package> package is not going to be upgraded and that it "
#~ "won't get security support after support for &oldreleasename; has been "
#~ "discontinued."
